<plot>Eddie Hawkes always feared a night like this. It's why he quit dealing meth two years ago. It's why he demanded his best friend, Danny Del Toro, leave behind the mean streets of Spokane's Lower South Hill. And it's why he conceded his territory to his former partner, Aaron Nash. Unfortunately for Eddie, his decisions weren't enough to avoid tonight. Tonight, Eddie's only choices are the hard ones.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?478611</url></doc>
